      "column": "left",
      "text": "Teem buhs fatwain Dee-\nwann fwehteem buht/ un fawa\nDeewa Wahrdu teem ne buhs\nfagahniht/ jo tee uppure ta KUN-\nGA Uggunis/ fawa Deewa\nMaisi/ tapehz buhs teem fweh-\nteem buht.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 7,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Weennu Manfu jeb Apfinee-\ntu teem ne buhs xemt/ nedz wee-\nnu Seeiwu/ kas no fawaWihra\natstahdinata irr/ teem ne buhs\nxemt/ jo tas irr fawam Deewam\nfwehts.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 8,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tapehz buhs tew to fweh-\ntiht/ jo wiꞥſch uppure tawa Dee-\nwa Maisi/ tam buhs tew fweh-\ntam buht/ jo es eſmu fwehts/ Es\ntas KUNGS/ kas juhs fwehti.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 9,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Ja nu kahda Preestera\nMeita eesahk Mauzibu dsibt/ ta\nfagahna fawu Tehwu/ ar Ugguni\nbuhs to fadefsinaht.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 10,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un tas/ kas Augsts-Pree-\nsteris irr starp farveem Brahkeem/\nus furra Galwu ta Swaidifcha-\nnas-Etje irr isleeta/ un ka Roh-\nka pildita tohp/ tam ne buhs fa-\nwu Galwu atfegt/ un fawas\nDrehbes ne faplohtiht.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 11,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tam arri ne buhs pee kah-\nda Mirroxa nahkt/ ir pahr fa-\nwu Tehwu/ un fawu Mahti tam\nne buhs nefchkihtu darritees.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 12,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un no fwehtas Weetas\ntam ne buhs iseet/ ka tas fawa\nDeewa fwehtu Weetu ne tagah-\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 13,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tam buhs arri weeni\nJumprawnu par Seeiwu xemt.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 14,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Weenu Atritni/ jeb At-\nstahdinatu/ jeb apsmeetu Man-\nfu/ tahdn tam ne buhs xemt/ be-\nweenu Jumprawnu no farveem\nLaudiin buhs winnam par See-\nwu xemt.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 15,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tam ne buhs fatwu Dsim-\nmunu starp farveem Laudim fa-\ngahniht/ jo esefnu tas KUNgs/\nkas winan fwehti.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 16,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un tas KUNGS runna-\nja us Mohsu/ un fazzija.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 17,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Runna us Aaronu un fak-\nki: Ne weenam no tawa Dsim-\nmuna juhsu Raddôs/ kam kah-\nda Waina buhs/ buhs pee-eet fa-\nwa Deewa Maisi uppureht.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 18,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Jo ne weenam Wihran/\nkam jeb kahda Waina irr buhs\npee-eet/ jepschu tas irr afis/ jeb\ntiflis/ jeb ar nejanku Degunu/\njeb kam wairak Lohzektu ne ka-\nwatjaga.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 19,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Jeb weens kam Kahja jeb\nRohka luhsusi.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 20,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Jeb Knpris/ jeb ar wah-\njahm Azzim/ jeb kam Ahda pahr\nAzz irr/ jeb kam Kraupis/ jeb/\nkam Kaschkis irr/ jeb kas Kaunu-\nma maitahts.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 21,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Ne weenam Wihran no\nAaronu ta Preestera Dsimmu-\nma/ kam jebkahda Waina irr\nbuhs pee-eet/ tohs Uggunis\npreefsch ta KUNGA nest/ win-\nram\n"
    }
